                <h3 class="title">Wireframing</h3>

                In terms of the user interface, wireframes have helped me
                to iterate over certain layouts and modules.
                The goal was to make the user journey as short as possible and only present key information at a time.
                Since the target platform is touch devices use of gestures should aid the overall interaction.
            </figcaption>
        </figure>
