</section>

<section id="visual-design" class="project-section--double-image">
    <article class="container">
        <figure>
            <img src="/images/adidas/slide_02.jpg" alt="">
            <img src="/images/adidas/visual-01.png" alt="">
            <figcaption>
                <h3 class="title">Visual design</h3>

                The goal for visual style and overall atmosphere was to keep things simple and emphasise any controls used to interact, like sliders and buttons when submitting results of an activity.
                The cards would be designed, following the conventions of original trading cards - athlete's picture and a table with personal goals.
                Any gamification elements and iconogrpahy is simplified and colourful.
            </figcaption>
        </figure>
    </article>
</section>

